<plot>The London Lesbian and Gay Switchboard opened in 1974 and 30 years later the switchboard remains one of the most active resources of this type anywhere in the world. In this short Switchboard Volunteers recount tales from their calls that paint an interesting picture of the London Gay Scene during this period.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?095312</url></doc>
